# Sims Overlay

A browser-based animated overlay featuring Sims-style characters built with Three.js.

## Disclaimer
I do not own any of the models used in this project. All characters and their respective assets belong to their original creators.

## Model Credits
All Models are Ripped by Centrixe (previously Tiramisu6) @ The Models Resource.
